title: Sons of Anarchy - Season 1 Complete
description:
ok so first thing: don't judge this show before you watch it. i know, first thing i heard was motorcycle gang, and i stopped listening. just didn't care.

and turns out it's completely awesome! copious amounts of badassery. lethal dose of dark humour. at least watch the first episode, you'll probably get hooked. and it's got ron perlman in it, how could it possibly be bad?

very vague description:

a man in his early 30s struggles to find a balance in his life between being a new dad and his involvement in a motorcycle gang. really it's mostly to do with beating the sh*t out of as many people as possible.

and i learned most torrents had poor quality episodes 1-3 so i took care of it.

and comment after you watch episode 8! you'll see what i mean. how f*cked up was that?

like usual, contains english subtitles.

full 13 episode first season.
